521
00:33:01,730 --> 00:33:03,595
You idiot!

522
00:33:03,690 --> 00:33:05,021
You!

523
00:33:05,108 --> 00:33:08,191
- Mom!
- I'm not your mom anymore.

524
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:11,687
