shut down the restaurant!

528
00:33:20,499 --> 00:33:23,411
Starting tomorrow,
just play ball then!

529
00:33:23,502 --> 00:33:27,040
Mom, you don't know a thing.

530
00:33:27,130 --> 00:33:29,041
