585
00:36:19,344 --> 00:36:20,800
- We've got a big problem!
- What is it?.

586
00:36:20,929 --> 00:36:23,090
It's Hyung-sik and
Yeon-hee!

587
00:36:23,264 --> 00:36:25,676
- What?.
- Come on! Hurry!

588
00:36:25,809 --> 00:36:27,674
They're in fight.

589
